    "description": "Titian's sensuous reclining nude gazes directly at the viewer with confident self-possession, holding a posy of roses in one hand. The warm, luminous flesh tones are set against rich fabrics — rumpled white sheets, a deep green curtain, and a rose-patterned couch. The domestic background with servants searching a cassone grounds the mythological subject in the intimacy of a Venetian palazzo.",
